OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome areas of cloud to start
OL,6,Fthe morning, mainly affecting higher
OL,7,Fground of Yorkshire, with possible
OL,8,Fearly mist and light rain over hills.
OL,9,FTurning mostly sunny by the afternoon.
OL,10,FFeeling hot by afternoon. Slightly
OL,11,Fcooler over the Derbyshire Hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine night with mostly
OL,14,Fclear skies across the region. Some
OL,15,Fcloud possible later in the night
OL,16,Facross higher ground. Winds remaining
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
