OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA similar day to Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine and turning
OL,7,Fhot or very hot by afternoon. Winds
OL,8,Fremaining light.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,11,Fdry and sunny with hot afternoons.
OL,12,FChance of isolated thundery showers at
OL,13,Ffirst, mainly affecting hills.
OL,14,FFreshening north-easterly breeze by
OL,15,FSunday. Temperatures above average
OL,16,Fthroughout.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
